description: Kalamas Local Grind is serving the streets of Maui! The offer a diverse menu of Home Cooked Local Food! Items include Ribeye, Burgers, Fresh Fish, Garlic fried Noodles, Kalua Pork, and many other Hawaiian favorites. Kamalas is adding Brown Rice as a choice for a healthier meal. Green salad is also available with their sweet garlic chili dressing. Check in often for local specials.
name: Kalamas Local Grinds
